73 LLVMBool LLVMVerifyModule(LLVMModuleRef M, LLVMVerifierFailureAction Action,
74  char **OutMessages) {
75  std::string Messages;
76 
77  LLVMBool Result = verifyModule(*unwrap(M),
78  static_cast<VerifierFailureAction>(Action),
79  OutMessages? &Messages : 0);
80 
81  if (OutMessages)
82  *OutMessages = strdup(Messages.c_str());
83 
84  return Result;
85 }
